{"tid":936381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己好失敗","createTime":"2018-12-10T16:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T10:58:43.000Z","uid":63313,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"42ede3d53fd4323151525bf095afaed35a377a08","tid":936381,"uid":63313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:54:36.000Z","msg":"之前第一次約咗個女仔出街<br />\n都知道衰緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見完之後佢whatsapp都唔覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀書方面雖然叫做有啲小聰明<br />\n但自己份人懶到仆街<br />\n乜撚嘢都高不成低不就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時候都幾羨慕啲背後有悲慘故事嘅人<br />\n因為佢地可以攞正牌唔開心<br />\n如果我同啲frd講自己唔開心<br />\n一定淨係會畀佢地笑鳩我喺到無病呻吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單身咗十幾年了<br />\n自己又唔識講嘢<br />\n身邊個個frd都有另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家淨係想有個人可以畀啲動力我去生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b69655173e6b022851a3b5226c9d3535d81326","tid":936381,"uid":186020,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"唸下屋企人"},{"pid":"e26c77a02973ada956b3a0ad23fd6d663ae3cf1b","tid":936381,"uid":186020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗下屋企人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"da9a406b3a47b38d3a961cbe6381ab60489c6334","tid":936381,"uid":63313,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"我諗可能等我老竇老母走咗 我都唔玩人生依個遊戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e9b708e57b810bf444a7e82431d0fc3ecd7b17","tid":936381,"uid":88782,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"溝唔到女就要生要死 垃撚圾"},{"pid":"f8abaa01368631c222145ee0c8c7f185f61b2f6b","tid":936381,"uid":63313,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":